            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:35:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Raider 18 HX AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 5090]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285875</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>MSI 在 CES 2025 发表全新手提电脑 Raider 18 HX AI，搭载 Nvidia RTX 5090 GPU 现时最火热的高阶图像处理器，再加上 Intel Core Ultra 285HX 处理器，硬件性能达到全新极限。18 吋 Mini-LED 显示屏具备 UHD+ 解像度、120Hz 更新率及 VESA DisplayHDR 1000 认证，无论是游戏还是创意工作均表现出色。电脑还内置有 AI 功能，特别是 AI Robot 助理与 AI Noise Cancellation Pro 技术，进一步提升用户体验。今次我们记者 Edward 就到现场为大家直击这部新机。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v.jpg 700w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>极致高性能 + 极致显示技术</h2><p>Raider 18 HX AI 配备 18 吋 Mini-LED 显示屏，解像度达到 UHD+（3840×2400 像素），并支援 120Hz 更新率和 VESA DisplayHDR 1000 认证。提供流畅画面表现，更达到 100% 接近 DCI-P3 色域覆盖，令暗部细节和色彩表现极致出众。不论是进行高需求游戏还是影像制作，都可提供专业级视觉体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285876 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>电脑内置流动版 Nvidia RTX 5090 GPU 配备 24GB GDDR7 记忆体，支援实时光线追踪和 DLSS 技术，能应对最新游戏的高画质需求。同时其强大硬件设计更满足专业影像处理与建模需求，为创作者和玩家带来强效支援。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285906" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412-662x580.jpg" alt="" width="662" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412-662x580.jpg 662w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412.jpg 1027w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 662px" /></p><h2>AI 技术助力效率提升</h2><p>Raider 18 HX AI 配备了 AI Robot 助理，采用小型语言模型技术，支持文字指令操控，方便用户快速完成应用程式启动或系统设定修改。AI Noise Cancellation Pro 则能有效消除背景噪音，特别适用于线上会议或游戏直播等需要高音质环境的场合。这些 AI 功能令使用者操作更加直观高效，同时提高生产力和便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285905" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418-651x580.jpg" alt="" width="651" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418-651x580.jpg 651w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418.jpg 1011w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 651px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
