        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】无内置电池、毋须充电的无线键盘   Lenovo 新产品可靠环境光供电</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/wirelesskeyboard/notebook/notebook-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wirelesskeyboard</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/wirelesskeyboard/notebook/notebook-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:29:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Notebook 配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285843</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>好多无线键盘用家，都要不时为键盘充电或更换电池，而 Lenovo 在 CES 2025 消费科技展就展示了一款 Self-Charging Bluetooth Keyboard 蓝牙键盘，抛弃了传统电池设计，透过光电面板和环境光线实现自我充电，成为科技与环保的融合。我们就等记者 Edward 带大家一齐到现场睇睇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403-694x440.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403-694x440.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>键盘核心技术在于结合光伏发电与超级电容器。键盘顶部设有高效能光电面板，可持续吸收太阳光或室内环境光，并通过超级电容器储存能量。相比传统的锂电池，超级电容器拥有更长的寿命，能承受数十万次充放电循环，而锂电池通常仅能维持约五年。</p><p>自充电键盘的设计亦相当实用与现代化。键盘为全尺寸设计，具有抗泼洒功能和三区域布局，方便用户进行自订设置。同时产品支援蓝牙连接，最多可连接三部装置，亦提供 USB-C 连接选项，该连接口隐藏于键盘顶部可拆卸盖内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816-430x580.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816-430x580.jpg 430w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816.jpg 668w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 430px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合 App 可了解键盘目前感光的程度</p><figure id="attachment_1285851" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1285851" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1285851" class="wp-caption-text">▲我们的记者用手指遮敝感应器的情况下，程式感应的光度会自然变得较小</figcaption></figure><p>这款键盘还可以搭配 Lenovo Accessories and Display Manager 应用程式使用，用户可在萤幕上查看亮度指示以及即时电力状态。无需更换电池的设计，除减少电子垃圾的产生，亦为用户省下额外成本，对环保与经济效益均带来正面影响。</p><p>多年来，我们已见过多种太阳能设备，但仅近年才有实用的替代方案出现，例如染料敏化太阳能电池等新技术。虽然这些技术距离用于笔记型电脑或手机仍需时日，但对于键盘与滑鼠等小型装置，却已显得成熟可行。</p><p>资料来源：Unwire.hk</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/wirelesskeyboard/notebook/notebook-parts/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple 明年或出折叠芒 iPhone，供应链消息 Samsung 供应最少 1600 万个荧幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/apple-fold-iphone/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-fold-iphone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/apple-fold-iphone/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[折叠荧幕]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285780</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>据外媒报导，Apple 正在积极开发折叠式 iPhone，并计划于明年第三季度正式推出。据悉这款折叠手机的显示荧幕将由 Samsung 提供，预计荧幕出货量为 1600 万至 2200 万，而 Apple 也已申请了相关的折叠式 iPhone 专利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/foldableiphone-694x465.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/foldableiphone-694x465.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/foldableiphone.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 申请的相关专利，图片来源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/iphone-flip-the-apple-foldable-may-still-be-coming-as-competition-grows/">CNET</a></p><p>自折叠手机问世以来，显示荧幕中间常会出现明显的折痕，尽管最近 Samsdung Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Galaxy Z Flip 6 有所改进，但目前仍然未能完全解决这个问题。据报折叠式 iPhone 外观将如 Galaxy Z Flip 相近，而根据《CNET》报道， Apple 正在积极寻求技术突破，以解决显示荧幕折痕问题，期望提供更完美的显示效果。</p><p>若 Apple 能够突破技术难关，将有望与 Samsung 等竞争对手一较高下。由于折叠显示荧幕成本较高，预计 Apple 折叠手机的售价亦会相应提高。市场上对折叠手机的需求逐步增长，而随著技术的成熟，未来几年内折叠手机将可能成为主流。Apple 作为全球最具影响力的科技企业，其推出折叠手机将对市场产生深远影响。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/iphone-flip-the-apple-foldable-may-still-be-coming-as-competition-grows/">CNET</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
